author: Brandy Zadrozny
title: Who owns coronavirus.com? Behind the lucrative profiteering on website domains
description: "People have this idea that you shouldn't profit on the tragedy," one domain seller said. "I think that's kind of a superstition.
content:
The coronavirus outbreak has spurred a rush on related website domain names such as coronavirus.com and stirred investors looking to profit off the newest global health crisis.
